articles.headline: Agent: Kuminga wants player option, would take qualifying offer
articles.description: Jonathan Kuminga's agent told ESPN that Kuminga -- who is seeking a player option -- is prepared to take the $8 million qualifying offer unless the Golden State Warriors improve their current offers.

images.name: Jonathan Kuminga [600x400]
images.caption: Jonathan Kuminga's agent told ESPN that the forward is prepared to take the $7.9 million qualifying offer unless the Golden State Warriors improve their current offers. Kuminga has been seeking a player option in the contract.

images.name: Chiney wants Warriors to get a deal done with Kuminga
images.caption: Chiney Ogwumike explains why she doesn't like the ongoing stalemate between the Warriors and restricted free agent Jonathan Kuminga.
